<!-- THE CHALLENGE -->
<p class="section-label cs-mb-24">/ The Challenge</p>
<h2 class="h2 cs-mb-24 cs-max-664">A blank sheet. One goal. An industry to disrupt.</h2>
<p class="body-lg cs-max-896 cs-mb-24">Bia Energy arrived with no brand, no identity, and no public presence. Entering a competitive clean energy market with a powerful commercial story, the challenge was to build a visual and verbal identity from scratch — one that balanced credibility and innovation without tipping into corporate blandness or greenwashing.</p>
<p class="body-lg cs-max-896 cs-section-gap">The brand had to work in a hi-vis jacket, on a conference stage, and in a B2B sales conversation — simultaneously.</p>

