<!-- THE SOLUTION -->
<p class="section-label cs-mb-24">/ The Solution</p>
<h2 class="h2 cs-mb-24 cs-max-664">The strategic foundation came first.</h2>
<p class="body-lg cs-max-896 cs-mb-24">The engagement opened with user persona research and a semi-fictional archetype model to map Bia Energy's B2B audience — demographics, psychographics, and decision-making behaviours. This fed a structured discovery workshop covering voice, values, and market positioning. Identity work began only once that foundation was in place.</p>
<p class="body-lg cs-max-896 cs-section-gap">I led the full creative direction from that point — designing every element of the brand: identity system, digital platform, marketing collateral, launch materials, and event production. I also shot all photography and video for the project, including aerial drone footage.</p>

