<!-- WHAT I DELIVERED -->
<p class="section-label cs-mb-24">/ What I Delivered</p>
<h2 class="h2 cs-mb-24 cs-max-664">End-to-end. From first brief to launch day.</h2>
<p class="body-lg cs-max-664 cs-mb-24">A full-lifecycle engagement — I held creative ownership across every layer of Bia Energy's public presence, from initial strategy through to launch week.</p>
<ul class="cs-deliverables cs-max-352 cs-mb-24">
  <li>Brand Identity &amp; Guidelines</li>
  <li>Content Creation</li>
  <li>Marketing Collateral</li>
  <li>Custom WordPress Build</li>
  <li>Carbon Calculator</li>
  <li>Launch Event</li>
  <li>AV &amp; Photography</li>
  <li>Conference Materials</li>
</ul>
<p class="body-base cs-max-664 cs-section-gap">The website was built on a bespoke WordPress theme — no templates, no shortcuts. The carbon offset calculator was designed as a functional B2B sales tool, giving prospective clients a way to model their own energy savings directly in the browser.</p>

