<!-- OUTCOMES -->
<p class="section-label cs-mb-24">/ Outcomes</p>
<h2 class="h2 cs-max-664 cs-section-gap">A brand built for a national moment.</h2>

<div class="cs-grid-2 cs-section-gap">
  <div class="cs-card-block">
    <span class="cs-card-num">001</span>
    <span class="cs-card-title">Launched at national scale</span>
    <span class="cs-card-body">The official launch was attended by Minister for Agriculture, Food and the Marine Charlie McConalogue T.D. — a signal of the project's significance to Ireland's renewable energy sector.</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cs-card-block">
    <span class="cs-card-num">002</span>
    <span class="cs-card-title">A landmark energy partnership</span>
    <span class="cs-card-body">Launch day marked the announcement of a strategic partnership with Gas Networks Ireland, establishing Dublin's first direct Renewable Gas Entry Point — allowing biomethane produced from food waste to be injected directly into the national gas network.</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cs-card-block">
    <span class="cs-card-num">003</span>
    <span class="cs-card-title">New commercial service launched</span>
    <span class="cs-card-body">Bia Collect — Bia Energy's sales and collection service — was introduced to market as part of the same launch programme, with brand and collateral delivered in full.</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cs-card-block">
    <span class="cs-card-num">004</span>
    <span class="cs-card-title">2,000+ LinkedIn followers in 12 months</span>
    <span class="cs-card-body">The Bia Energy LinkedIn community reached 2,000 followers within the first year of operations — built entirely on the brand platform and content strategy established at launch.</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cs-card-block">
    <span class="cs-card-num">005</span>
    <span class="cs-card-title">Best in Class 2026</span>
    <span class="cs-card-body">Bia Energy has since been named Best in Class 2026 for Anaerobic Digestion on the island of Ireland.</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cs-card-block">
    <span class="cs-card-num">006</span>
    <span class="cs-card-title">Full creative ownership, one lead</span>
    <span class="cs-card-body">Strategy, identity, UX, build, photography, drone footage, launch event, and AV — conceived and delivered under one creative director.</span>
  </div>
</div>

